    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Oliver hall is no longer avail\nable for Elizabeth Gurley Flynn,\n1t is reported today that the local\nsocialist party has been notified by\nMr.. Oliver that unless the speeches\nof the woman leader are discon-\ntinued, the hall will be closed to\nthe socialists themselves.\n\n\nShe is scheduled to speak at the\nTurner hall on Wednesday night of\nthis week. On the last of the week\nshe leaves for an extended speak\ning tour in the mining region of\nBritish Columbia."
    }
